<html>
        <head>
                <title>MVC</title>
        </head>

        <body>

        MVC views end with .gspx extension <br/>
        MVC controllers are groovy scripts or classes.
        
                <form action="mvc.gspx" method="post">

                        <table>
                                <tr>
                                        <td colspan="2">${message}</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                        <td>First Name</td>
                                        <td><input type="text" name="firstName"> </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                        <td>Last Name</td>
                                        <td><input type="text" name="lastName"></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                        <td colspan="2"><input type="submit" name="submit" value="Submit"></td>
                                </tr>


                        </table>

                </form>

        </body>
</html>